      • publish

        void publish(ICDOTransactionAggregator aggregator,
             java.lang.String toolingId,
             PublishOperationConfiguration configuration,
             org.eclipse.core.runtime.IProgressMonitor monitor)
      throws SnowowlServiceException
        Performs the publication based on the configuration argument.
        Parameters:
        aggregator - the aggregator where the dirty transaction has to be stored after adjusting components and before commit.
        toolingId - the tooling ID the current publish manager responsible for.
        configuration - the configuration for the operation.
        monitor - monitor for the publication process.
        Throws:
        SnowowlServiceException - if the publication failed.
